{"tid":2167343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣國防部發布影片「好戰必亡，忘戰必危」","createTime":"2020-08-21T05:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T13:52:44.000Z","uid":337052,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"51ff93d7eda52dd16b5694c40d2a4393c052ff94","tid":2167343,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>國防部發布影片 有信心確保國家安全[影]</strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/08/21 10:50<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200821/800x600_44893006169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200821%2F800x600_44893006169.jpg&h=b5240364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國防部20日晚間在臉書發布「好戰必亡，忘戰必危」影片，並表示對於近期中共解放軍各種軍事壓迫的作為，國防部表達嚴正態度，強調國軍從不挑釁、但也絕不示弱。（<a href=\"http://圖取自facebook.com/MilitarySpokesman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAfacebook.com%2FMilitarySpokesman&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=7b282383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自facebook.com/MilitarySpokesman</a>）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者游凱翔台北20日電）中共近期頻機艦擾台，且透過官媒恫嚇台灣。國防部今天表示，最蠻橫的國家莫過輕易挑起戰端，最無知的政府則陷人民於戰火之中，面對中共一次次挑釁與恫嚇，只會讓國人更加緊密團結，認清中共窮兵黷武的本質。<br />\n<br />\n中共近期頻頻以機艦擾台，甚至不時侵犯台灣西南方防空識別區（ADIZ），且透過官媒恫嚇台灣。<br />\n<br />\n國防部晚間在臉書發布「好戰必亡，忘戰必危」影片，並表示，對於近期中共解放軍各種軍事壓迫的作為，國防部表達嚴正態度，強調國軍從不挑釁、但也絕不示弱，「絕對不要輕忽我們捍衛台灣的決心」。<br />\n<br />\n國防部強調，最蠻橫的國家莫過輕易挑起戰端，最無知的政府則陷人民於戰火之中。面對中共一次又一次的挑釁與恫嚇，只會讓國人更加的緊密團結，認清中共窮兵黷武的本質，既不尊重民意，且動輒訴諸戰爭的威懾行徑，終將適得其反，並已引起台灣人民的憤怒與反感，重傷海峽兩岸的和平穩定。<br />\n<br />\n國防部再次強調，國軍捍衛國家主權、守護民主，有信心、也有能力確保國家的安全。國軍就是國家最重要的穩定力量，也是軍人用生命盡忠的終身職志。（編輯：林興盟）1090820<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008200384.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202008200384.aspx&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=708e4340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008200384.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=638383123502001&amp;extid=7zlspib2yjgncu6H\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D638383123502001%26extid%3D7zlspib2yjgncu6H&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=9cb424ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=638383123502001&amp;extid=7zlspib2yjgncu6H</a>"},{"pid":"c79f98f848c9be533fafe0698c34c0e7f59ce19f","tid":2167343,"uid":135408,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:07:08.000Z","msg":"支持國民革命軍保家衛國"},{"pid":"5b4afa6b830695e0074124069109fd28388eb522","tid":2167343,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ece5c78cee7ec7ede86baa24bcb9e36f484d92ec","tid":2167343,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"c79f98f848c9be533fafe0698c34c0e7f59ce19f","tid":2167343,"uid":135408,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:07:08.000Z","msg":"支持國民革命軍保家衛國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"國民革命軍本身就係法西斯軍"},{"pid":"91be6ce6108c44bc3b3cbb9544ed60005ac46e2d","tid":2167343,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea45acad0473358a1c2d6b065ccb4d0589ba410","tid":2167343,"uid":337052,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ece5c78cee7ec7ede86baa24bcb9e36f484d92ec","tid":2167343,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"c79f98f848c9be533fafe0698c34c0e7f59ce19f","tid":2167343,"uid":135408,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:07:08.000Z","msg":"支持國民革命軍保家衛國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"國民革命軍本身就係法西斯軍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"台灣已經軍隊國家化<br />\n沒有革命軍"},{"pid":"cf9c3710cc8d16a771eee71bd8c0d790d2b5f80f","tid":2167343,"uid":220942,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"台灣文化水平高<br />\n8隻字講哂所有重點"},{"pid":"c7b954f6b7c9d1da89a4f224f18ad0072a8140bc","tid":2167343,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:16:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6VNjklrT7ks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6VNjklrT7ks&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=20c41ab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6VNjklrT7ks</a><br />\n漢光演習集錦"},{"pid":"7aa0aa48a4409cef9187a1d9ed6f223119f4b7b1","tid":2167343,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"共機趁阿薩爾訪台越界挑釁 美國「非常火大」南海即刻調動大軍反擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200821/FMNHQTY2ZRG5ZIOUAKMLWHVCFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200821%2FFMNHQTY2ZRG5ZIOUAKMLWHVCFM%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=84f24043\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200821%2FFMNHQTY2ZRG5ZIOUAKMLWHVCFM%2F&h=3925a8b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200821/FMNHQTY2ZRG5ZIOUAKMLWHVCFM/</a>"},{"pid":"3106a344a141a89eef46a818b193053337fdab8f","tid":2167343,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:27:27.000Z","msg":"台海軍情》E-2K預警機升級為E-2D 立委驚曝還有2項超級厲害功能<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/08/21/phpX4sIWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F08%2F21%2FphpX4sIWF.jpg&h=8568c340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國E-2D預警機，為美國海軍航空母艦的主力艦載預警機。（圖：擷取自美國海軍網站）<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-21 11:25:59<br />\n〔記者羅添斌／台北報導〕國防部動支15.1億台幣的經費，由美國為台灣空軍現役的6架E-2K預警機進行系統升級，完成之後將達到美軍現役航空母艦E-2D艦載預警機同等級性能，長期在立院外交國防委員會的立委王定宇更稱，E-2D可以協調戰區飛彈防禦系統，並助強台灣的飛彈反擊能力。<br />\n<br />\n立委王定宇在參加政論節目時，談及我國要將現役的6架E-2K預警機進行系統升級相關議題。他說，我國在1995年買了4架E-2T預警機，1999年又買了2架E-2K預警機，這是鷹眼2000型的外銷型，台灣這6架過去其實蠻夠用的，每一架可以探測的範圍是400公里到500公里，南北各放一架，兩岸之間，海峽跟台灣的縱深，大概都可以觀察丶指揮丶控制的到。<br />\n<br />\n但王定宇指出，這型機還不夠好，台灣一直希望能夠得到跟美軍現在所有航空母艦上的主力預警機，也就是E-2D（先進鷹眼 AHE），要了很久，美國過去沒有給我們，因為這個性能太先進，在美軍的福特號丶羅斯福號航空母艦上都可以看的到。<br />\n<br />\n王定宇說，先進鷹眼AHE過去一直拿不到，但在今年春天，台灣6架鷹眼機通通要更新改版丶結構更新，變成E-2D AHE，全部升級，金額只要15億而已。<br />\n<br />\n他說，我們最近買M1A2戰車丶F16V戰機，都是美國軍方幫我們下訂單，一毛不加轉給台灣，就是跟美軍同樣的價格，這6架E-2D AHE將來會有什麼樣的能力？除了增加對空目標的監控，濱海地區威脅的提早感知丶偵測能力的擴大之外，還有兩個別的地方，一個是可以協調戰區飛彈防禦系統，另外一個是協調空中來襲的各種預警之外，還有我們的反擊能力，其中包括中程飛彈。<br />\n<br />\n王定宇指出，中程飛彈在美軍的定義，是指1000公里到3000公里，日本沒有，所以美軍要放在那裡，「台灣有沒有，我不知道」，但在台灣加了E-2D之後，就可以指揮這些中程飛彈往哪裡飛，換成了E-2D之後，簡直就是把台灣做一艘超級無敵航空母艦一般。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3267075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3267075&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=df6e685f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3267075&h=ea76b516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3267075</a>"},{"pid":"0d37bd554203271126b6c5192911b5bd7b0596fb","tid":2167343,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"證明亞洲軍隊唔一定要好似支共果d咁柒"},{"pid":"97a6d31a06815b8ea35ef9e1d27e2e31991aa1a2","tid":2167343,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d37bd554203271126b6c5192911b5bd7b0596fb","tid":2167343,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"證明亞洲軍隊唔一定要好似支共果d咁柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7412e9518018ded619f256b29ce5e29fa25ea5e","tid":2167343,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"「搬石頭砸自己的腳」"},{"pid":"c29bfa504095f76de68234f53f0363c165b3797e","tid":2167343,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"支那唔輸得呢樣野我相信台灣更清楚"},{"pid":"7adcfc59cba2c4d380dd60ed64c213677d40cf3c","tid":2167343,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d7412e9518018ded619f256b29ce5e29fa25ea5e","tid":2167343,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"「搬石頭砸自己的腳」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mzPXpZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mzPXpZ.jpg&h=9ff2149a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a14003a98f34be7426b3479be4c6aff0f0996447","tid":2167343,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117e456d1ec8b033681da7fd11d07cabb40331fb","tid":2167343,"uid":212624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9313eeb8b8cf72fbcaadcb83442d7f9e2d00a380","tid":2167343,"uid":58209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:32:36.000Z","msg":"民主自由 堅守不退<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867093a9e73f86bb83e5f3ec8fc7e3bd1ed667c9","tid":2167343,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"台灣實彈練習都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c30ad2fa645375dc8c2596b8aa2836bab499e6","tid":2167343,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score